s/2024/12/18-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/18-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/18-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-120x80.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=773096\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-773096\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white photo of two boys near a stone wall. One boy, in the foreground, holds a toy gun and poses as if aiming. The other boy stands in silhouette, watching the first boy. Graffiti is visible on the wall.\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/09-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-120x80.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=773092\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-773092\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/05-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Two children stand in front of an ancient stone archway adorned with intricate carvings and inscriptions. The sunlight casts dramatic shadows, highlighting the ornate details of the architecture. The image is in black and white.\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" s