ading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"A black and white photo of a group of people walking down a narrow street, some carrying wooden crosses. The street is lined with stone buildings, and the sky appears clear. The mood is solemn and focused.\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/16-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-120x80.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=773093\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-773093\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Black and white image of a person walking on a cobblestone street in a shadowed alley. The individual wears a hat and long garment while holding an umbrella. Sunlight and shadows create contrasting patterns on the ground.\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-800x533.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/06-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-120x80.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=773095\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-773095\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-533x800.jpg\" alt=\"A black and white scene of an old stone courtyard with a small child pushing a stroller in the foreground. In the background, a woman stands near a door with two children. The buildings have arched windows and visible wiring.\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-533x800.jpg 533w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-213x320.jpg 213w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-1023x1536.jpg 1023w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08-Ofir.Barak-OCJ.jpg 1110w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=773107\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-773107\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/20-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-535x800.jpg\" alt=\"A black-and-white photo shows an old stone archway with a bird flying through it. Below, there is a glass display case containing a scroll and text written on a large plaque, flanked by two vertical wooden structures.\" width=\"535\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/20-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-535x800.jpg 535w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/20-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-214x320.jpg 214w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/20-Ofir.Barak-OCJ-1027x1536.jpg 1027w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/20-Ofir.Barak-OCJ.jpg 1114w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBarak decided to pursue photography in 2014 when he was gifted a Leica M240 and a 50mmm summicron lens by his grandmother. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“Looking back, deciding to pick up the rangefinder camera as a tool for my craft was a real milestone for me, it forced me to embrace its unique advantages and disadvantages,” he says. “I have stayed for the most part with this setup ever since.” \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBarak has since acquired the more technologically advanced \u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/2020/03/12/the-leica-m10-monochrom-is-great-not-in-spite-of-its-weaknesses-but-because-of-them/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eLeica M10 Monochrom \u003c/a\u003e but says the camera “bridges the gap between analog feel and digital photography.” \u003c/p\u003e\n \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eOld City Jerusalem\u003c/em\u003e is available now in hardback and can be purchased \u003ca href=\"https://www.ofirbarak.com/publications\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. More of the photographer’s work can be found on his \u003ca href=\"https://www.ofirbarak.com/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ewebsite\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ofirbarak/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e \u003chr/\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImage credits:\u003c/strong\u003e Photographs by Ofir Barak\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n          \n      \n\n              \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003ePetaPixel articles may include affiliate links; if you buy something through such a link, PetaPixel may earn a commission.\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \n    \n\n    \n          \n      \n\n\n\n\n  